shop.title: Adrianna's Bakery
shop.subtitle:
Welcome to Adrianna's Bakery! I'm a Black Baker located in Chico, CA.

I offer shipping to all states in the U.S.

Text (951-271-1868) or send a DM (@adriannas_bakery) your order and full name. Please indicate if you need it shipped and at what address. Lastly, indicate what date you will need your delicious order delivered by and an invoice will be sent your way.

shop.title: All Thingz Haute
shop.subtitle:
All Thingz Haute is a revolutionary brand whose motto is "The Art of Being Beautiful". We promise to keep empowering women everywhere to live their best life in a High Class Fashion.

Leveraging the awareness from her brand, Haute Headz, through All Thingz Haute is poised to become one of the most recognized names in the cosmetology industry.
